      "description": "This S54-powered legend offers a pure mechanical connection, featuring a 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and an 8,000 RPM redline. The dual-VANOS system has been recently calibrated for peak torque delivery across the rev range. Power is sent through a precise 6-speed manual to a variable M differential lock, ensuring exceptional corner-exit traction. The chassis remains taut with reinforced subframe mounts and refreshed bushings, maintaining the legendary 50/50 weight distribution and communicative steering rack that defines this era of performance engineering.",
