    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a 2019 Executive Series Sedan in a striking Graphite Grey Metallic. This vehicle has been a reliable daily driver and remains in solid mechanical and aesthetic shape. The interior features premium charcoal leather upholstery with genuine wood trim; the seats show minimal wear, and the cabin remains smoke-free. Powering the car is a responsive 2.0L turbocharged engine paired with an 8-speed automatic transmission that shifts effortlessly. Recent maintenance includes a fresh oil service, new engine air filters, and a coolant flush. The dual-zone climate control, heated steering wheel, and 10-inch touchscreen interface are all in perfect working order. On the exterior, the paint holds a deep gloss, though there are a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scratch near the passenger door handle consistent with careful use. The 19-inch alloy wheels are wrapped in Michelin all-season tires with roughly 65% tread remaining. This car offers a smooth, quiet ride and comes with a complete service history folder for your peace of mind.",
