    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring six individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing for optimized volumetric efficiency across the rev range. This example has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive valve lash adjustment. Power is delivered to the rear wheels via a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. The suspension geometry remains tight, utilizing MacPherson struts up front and a multi-link rear setup for exceptional turn-in response. While the exterior shows minor wear indicative of a well-loved driver's car, the powertrain maintains robust compression and peak cooling efficiency. Ideal for the enthusiast seeking a visceral, analog driving experience with a proven service history.",
